dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Sawyer County, Wisconsin in 2012. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Sawyer_Roads_2012.gdb.[The address range is a linear feature class that contains the high-low, left-right attributes for addresses. This feature class is used for geo coding and may also be used to support dispatching.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
